{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"笔〔对口词〕","authors":["杜景龙"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":6,"day":1}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"笔〔对口词〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天津市东郊区金谷小学六年级  杜景龙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：笔！是我们的学习工具，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：也是阶级斗争的武器。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：我们用笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：揭露剥削阶级的罪恶；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：我们用笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：记述劳动人民的悲惨遭遇；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：我们用笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：跟一切敌人斗争到底。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：旧社会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：笔杆握在地主、资本家手里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：他们用笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：作剥削穷人的工具。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：他们用笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：仗势把穷人欺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：农村里，地主的笔在账本上画一画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：农民们就得卖儿卖女。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：工厂里，资本家的笔动一动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：工人们就得饿肚皮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：笔啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：笔！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：解放以后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：你回到了劳动人民手里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：你记载了多少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：劳动人民的英雄事迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：你写出了劳动人民的心意："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：“万岁共产党！万岁毛主席！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：我们要做——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：工人阶级和贫下中农的好儿女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：要紧握着笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：努力学习。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：用优良的成绩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：向党献礼！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}